# ğŸŒ±The Quanli of the Carrier

The carrier, as a reality existence, possesses Quanli in two layers of meaning:

1.The carrier as Tianran Quanli of â€œexistence itselfâ€
The carrier is reality existence; the carrier itself is Quanli; the carrier is the Quanli subject.
The carrier's Quanli is identical to that of any other existence: it can manifest continuously without consciousness, and it can self-define and self-converge without consciousness.
Its naturalness is a priori existence. Its absorption of quota, maintenance of structure, and termination of self-sustenance are all â€œbeing what it is.â€ For example, a seed possesses the Quanli to germinateâ€”this has nothing to do with whether it will germinate, whether someone plants it, or whether there is sunlight. This Quanli is already determined as existence the moment the structure forms.
Learning, self, and aspiration are the unfolding forms of life as existence itself; they are the natural disposition of life, and thus the Tianran Quanli of the life carrier.
Occupying spacetime, consuming energy, being constrained by physical laws, and participating in entropy increase settlement are the carrier's natural attributes and thus its Tianran Quanli.
Pain, fatigue, coma, collapse, termination, and even death are the carrier's naturally determined structural certaintiesâ€”Tianran Quanliâ€”not passive reactions to any external or internal manifestation.
Gravity, entropy increase, DNA replication, chemical reactions, galaxy formationâ€¦ these variations and iterations within existing structures, whether self-converging or open, are Tianran Quanli.
As one member among them, the carrier also possesses the Tianran Quanli of self-constraint, ceasing expansion, contracting creation, returning to stability, self-definition, and renouncing transcendence.

2.The carrier's structural Quanli in relation to consciousness
â‘  Quanli of use in relation to consciousness:
In the process of consciousness defining, cutting, and assigning value in narration, the carrier possesses the Quanli of use; the carrier also possesses the Quanli of use regarding any new Quanli created by consciousness.
Consciousness's outputs only become actual Quanli when enacted through carrier action.
â‘¡ The sole settlement Quanli for paying the physical quota on behalf of consciousness:
Consciousness can design infinite narratives: every thought consumes metabolism, every emotion alters endocrinology, every choice traverses neural pathways. Narratives that cannot be settled will be settled through anxiety, depression, psychopathology, and physiological breakdownâ€”this is not moral judgment, but structural necessity.
â‘¢ Bandwidth Quanli for bearing consciousness:
The carrier has upper limits on attention, memory, and energy, which determine how much information consciousness can process simultaneously, how high a density of self-reference it can sustain, and how long it can endure abstract computation.

Conclusion:
The carrier's Quanli is the Quanli of existence itself. It possesses the Quanli to refuse excessive manifestation, to forcibly settle conscious behavior, and to respond with collapse or termination.
In the world defined by consciousness, the carrier has the Quanli to decide whether this world merits continuation / is worth sustaining.


